<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jul 2026 02:37:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国会提议的特朗普级战舰计划护栏遭到白宫抵制</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/congress-proposed-trump-class-battleship-program-guardrails-met-with-white-house-pushback</link><description>&lt;p&gt;国会正在推进一项法案，该法案将阻止特朗普级战舰的建造，除非某些武器被认为已经成熟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/congress-proposed-trump-class-battleship-program-guardrails-met-with-white-house-pushback"&gt;国会提出的特朗普级战舰计划护栏遭到白宫抵制后，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 23:14:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/congress-proposed-trump-class-battleship-program-guardrails-met-with-white-house-pushback</guid></item><item><title>直升机刚刚在环太平洋沉没演习中占据中心舞台</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/helicopters-just-took-center-stage-in-rim-of-the-pacific-sinking-exercises</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在大规模的太平洋演习中，盟军旋翼机至少使用了四种不同类型的导弹来对抗退役战舰。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/helicopters-just-took-center-stage-in-rim-of-the-pacific-sinking-exercises"&gt;直升机刚刚在环太平洋沉没演习中占据中心舞台的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 22:34:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/helicopters-just-took-center-stage-in-rim-of-the-pacific-sinking-exercises</guid></item><item><title>伊朗威胁攻击英国空军基地，EA-37B 抵达英国皇家空军费尔福德</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ea-37bs-arrive-at-raf-fairford-as-iran-threatens-to-attack-the-uk-air-base</link><description>&lt;p&gt;英国皇家空军费尔福德空军基地是美国空军轰炸机执行针对伊朗和其他飞往中东的飞机执行任务的主要枢纽。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ea-37bs-arrive-at-raf-fairford-as-iran-threatens-to-attack-the-uk-air-base"&gt;伊朗威胁攻击英国空军基地后，EA-37B 战机抵达英国皇家空军费尔福德基地&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 19:31:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ea-37bs-arrive-at-raf-fairford-as-iran-threatens-to-attack-the-uk-air-base</guid></item><item><title>美国陆军数十年来首次购买较旧的 PAC-2 爱国者导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-army-is-buying-older-pac-2-patriot-missiles-for-the-first-time-in-decades</link><description>&lt;p&gt;PAC-2 GEM-T 导弹的能力总体上不如 PAC-3 导弹，但陆军需要它能获得的所有爱国者导弹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-army-is-buying-older-pac-2-patriot-missiles-for-the-first-time-in-decades"&gt;美国陆军数十年来首次购买较旧的 PAC-2 爱国者导弹&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 18:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-army-is-buying-older-pac-2-patriot-missiles-for-the-first-time-in-decades</guid></item><item><title>空对地能力已经渗透到 F-15EX 的任务中</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set</link><description>&lt;p&gt;F-15EX 目前的任务与其前身 F-15C 相同，都是严格的空对空作战，但这种情况将会改变。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set"&gt;空对地能力已经渗透到 F-15EX 的任务集中&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 23:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/air-to-ground-capabilities-are-already-creeping-into-the-f-15exs-mission-set</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装现在在红海袭击沙特油轮，对能源供应造成重大影响（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications</link><description>&lt;p&gt;就在与伊朗的战争即将再次全面爆发之际，胡塞武装将进一步挤压世界能源供应。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications"&gt;胡塞武装现在在红海袭击沙特油轮，对能源供应造成重大影响（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 23:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/houthis-now-attacking-saudi-oil-tankers-in-red-sea-major-energy-supply-implications</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰F-16首次空对空击落俄罗斯战斗机：美国高级将领</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general</link><description>&lt;p&gt;丹·凯恩将军的披露证实了乌克兰 F-16 本月击落一架俄罗斯 Su-35S 的报道。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general"&gt;乌克兰 F-16 对俄罗斯战斗机首次空对空击落：美国高级将军&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 18:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ukrainian-f-16-scored-first-air-to-air-kill-against-a-russian-fighter-top-u-s-general</guid></item><item><title>Brontanax 战斗机无人机是英国向协作战斗机迈进的一大步</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft</link><description>&lt;p&gt;BAE Systems 刚刚推出了具有一些有趣功能的隐形 CCA。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;博文&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft"&gt;《Brontanax 战斗机无人机是英国协作战斗机的大跃进》&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 17:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/brontanax-fighter-drone-is-the-uks-big-leap-into-collaborative-combat-aircraft</guid></item><item><title>海军选择 RAACM-ER 低成本巡航导弹用于帮助武装盟友的计划（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies</link><description>&lt;p&gt;CHAOS计划旨在为友军地面部队提供新的、更便宜的方法来远距离攻击陆地上的船只和目标。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies"&gt;海军选择 RAACM-ER 低成本巡航导弹用于帮助武装盟友的计划（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 17:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-picks-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-for-program-to-help-arm-allies</guid></item><item><title>海军寻求母舰用于南方司令部行动</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations</link><description>&lt;p&gt;该船将能够发射和回收直升机、无人机和小船，并充当海上行动基地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations"&gt;海军为南方司令部行动寻找母舰后&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 16:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/mothership-sought-by-navy-for-southern-command-operations</guid></item></channel></rss>